          "slidecontent": "• Guest data is sensitive and deserves careful handling every time\n• AI tools can process personal, travel, and payment data in ways that are not always visible\n• Always follow your organisation's data privacy policies before sharing guest information with any system\n• When in doubt, less is more\n• Report concerns about data misuse to your manager or data protection officer promptly\n• Review your workplace's AI usage guidelines as a practical next step"
